	<Title>
		Uterine fibroids treatment: Focused ultrasound
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Uterine fibroids treatment with MRI and ultrasound &amp;mdash; relief is possible without surgery or drugs.
	</Abstract>
	<Stream>
		<VideoFile>
			/video/streams/mm00705.wmv
		</VideoFile>
